INSERT INTO item(item_id,store_id,item_name,price,description,photo,remain) VALUES ('i46','s1','Halo 5: Guardians (Xbox One) - Walmart.com',39.88,'A mysterious and unstoppable force threatens the galaxy, the Master Chief is missing and his loyalty questioned. Experience the most dramatic Halo story to date in a 4-player cooperative epic that spans three worlds. Challenge friends and rivals in new multiplayer.*','de6eee21-fc60-11e5-bf06-a088697ea576.jpg',38);
INSERT INTO item(item_id,store_id,item_name,price,description,photo,remain) VALUES ('i47','s1','Xbox One Elite Wireless Controller - Walmart.com',149.00,'Bring your gaming experience to the next level of intensity with the Microsoft Xbox One Elite Wireless Controller. It features an abundance of swappable components, Hair Trigger Locks and nearly limitless customization. You can choose from a variety of thumbsticks, D-pads and paddles for a tailored feel. This wireless game controller delivers game-changing accuracy and speed. Use the Hair Trigger Locks to fire faster and improve your control with interchangeable paddles and a rubberized diamond grip. Designed for the serious gamer, the Microsoft Xbox One Elite Wireless Controller brings all the features together with an easy-to-use app. Use it to tweak anything from trigger sensitivity to button mapping. Additionally, you can store up to 14 inputs to your components. Keep your eyes on the game and let your fingers perform flawlessly with the customized controller of your design.','def89080-fc60-11e5-8f4c-a088697ea576.jpg',42);
INSERT INTO item(item_id,store_id,item_name,price,description,photo,remain) VALUES ('i48','s1','Call Of Duty Black Ops III (Xbox One) - Walmart.com',39.88,'Call of Duty: Black Ops III deploys its players into a future where bio-technology has enabled a new breed of Black Ops soldier. Players are now always on and always connected to the intelligence grid and their fellow operatives during battle. In a world more divided than ever, this elite squad consists of men and women who have enhanced their combat capabilities to fight faster, stronger, and smarter. Every soldier has to make difficult decisions and visit dark places in this engaging, gritty narrative.','df6e35b0-fc60-11e5-bb1e-a088697ea576.jpg',33);
INSERT INTO item(item_id,store_id,item_name,price,description,photo,remain) VALUES ('i49','s1','Xbox One Kinect Sensor with Dance Central Spotlight - Walmart.com',99.00,'Step up your gaming experience with the Xbox One Kinect Sensor With Dance Central Spotlight. This add-on device allows you to command your Xbox and TV with your voice and movements, play games where you are the controller, and even make Skype calls in HD. Be recognized and get signed-in automatically when using your voice to find your favorite entertainment and snap apps. The Xbox One sensor also allows you to record game clips and broadcast your play live with the picture-in-picture feature. Kinect has a high resolution full HD camera, advanced infrared technology and a microphone array with noise isolation for maximum precision in capturing sound and motion. Also included in this video game sensor package is a token to download the newest game in the Dance Central series -- the Dance Central Spotlight.','e00c2361-fc60-11e5-8fa9-a088697ea576.jpg',9);
INSERT INTO item(item_id,store_id,item_name,price,description,photo,remain) VALUES ('i50','s1','Forza Motorsport 6 (Xbox One) - Walmart.com',38.97,'Unrelenting action at simulation speed in the most beautiful and comprehensive racing game of this generation. Collect, customize, and race over 450 Forzavista cars, all with working cockpits and full damage. Compete in epic 24-player races across 26 world-famous locales. Master wet weather and night racing on your road to victory.','e097736e-fc60-11e5-954f-a088697ea576.jpg',16);
INSERT INTO item(item_id,store_id,item_name,price,description,photo,remain) VALUES ('i51','s1','Minecraft (Xbox One) - Walmart.com',17.57,'If you can imagine it, you can build it! Minecraft, the best-selling game on Xbox 360, is coming to Xbox One. Create and explore your very own world where the only limit is what you can imagine - just be sure to build a shelter when night comes to stay safe from monsters. Play on your own or join up to 8 friends in split screen mode.','e1353a0f-fc60-11e5-9134-a088697ea576.jpg',17);
INSERT INTO item(item_id,store_id,item_name,price,description,photo,remain) VALUES ('i52','s1','Microsoft Forza Motorsport 6 - Racing Game - Xbox One (rk2-0001) - Walmart.com',60.86,'<p>Forza Motorsport 6 <br/><br/>From the creators of the best-selling Xbox racing series comes the follow-up to the 2013 DICE Racing Game of the Year. Collect, customize, and race the cars of your dreams, including the video game debut of the Ford GT</p>','e23014d1-fc60-11e5-a5db-a088697ea576.jpg',50);
INSERT INTO item(item_id,store_id,item_name,price,description,photo,remain) VALUES ('i53','s1','Rise of the Tomb Raider (Xbox One) - Walmart.com',38.59,'After uncovering an ancient mystery, Lara Croft embarks on a journey throughout the most treacherous and remote regions of the world to find the secret of immortality. Forming powerful new alliances and relying on her intellect and survival skills, Lara will ultimately embrace her fate as the Tomb Raider. Featuring epic, high-octane action moments set in the most beautifully hostile environments on earth, Rise of the Tomb Raider delivers a cinematic survival action adventure where you will join Lara Croft on her first tomb raiding expedition and witness the rise of an icon.','e3005d1e-fc60-11e5-9145-a088697ea576.jpg',15);
INSERT INTO item(item_id,store_id,item_name,price,description,photo,remain) VALUES ('i54','s1','Xbox One Play and Charge Kit - Walmart.com',23.65,'Keep the action going with the Xbox One Play and Charge Kit. Recharge while you play or afterwards, even when your Xbox is in standby. The long-lasting rechargeable battery fully charges in under four hours. Say goodbye to disposable batteries and having to swap them out in the middle of a game.','e390410f-fc60-11e5-948a-a088697ea576.jpg',21);
INSERT INTO item(item_id,store_id,item_name,price,description,photo,remain) VALUES ('i55','s1','Xbox One 500GB Gears of War Bundle with Arkham Knight &amp; 8 in 1 Kit - Walmart.com',479.99,'Introducing Xbox One. Where the best games, multiplayer, and your favorite movies, music, sports and live TV come together in one place. Xbox One games look and feel incredibly real, with cinematic gameplay that rivals Hollywood. Watch TV or chat with friends on Skype while you play, and keep on playing while smarter matchmaking happens behind the scenes. With Xbox One, you can snap two things side-by-side on your TV, and switch from one to another instantly. Cloud-powered and built for the digital age, Xbox One is designed to keep getting better over time. Xbox One delivers an all-new gaming and entertainment experience that will transform how you play. Xbox One brings together the best games, the most reliable service and rich entertainment all-in-one system that is built for today and tomorrow.<br/><br/>* 8 Cores: An 8-core x86 processor lets you instantly switch between a game and your favorite entertainment apps with ease<br/><br/>* HDMI Pass-Thru: Connect your cable or satellite box to your Xbox One and prepare for lift off. HDMI pass-thru enables you to watch TV through your Xbox, which makes switching inputs seem almost pre-historic.<br/><br/>* Loaded with memory: 8GB of RAM and a 500GB hard drive give you plenty of memory for your games, demos, movies, apps, music, and more.<br/>* Blu-ray: Watch movies and play games in stunning HD with a Blu-ray player.<br/><br/>* Kinect or Controller: There are a variety of ways to interact with Xbox One. Depending on the game or app, you can control Xbox One using voice commands and gestures, a controller, a remote control or your Xbox One SmartGlass device. It is designed to interact with you in multiple ways.<br/><br/>* Play Xbox One games online or offline: Your Xbox One does not','e40fd14f-fc60-11e5-8626-a088697ea576.jpg',14);
INSERT INTO item(item_id,store_id,item_name,price,description,photo,remain) VALUES ('i56','s1','Tom Clancy&#39;s The Division (Xbox One) - Walmart.com',59.00,'Tom Clancy&#39;s The Division is a ground-breaking RPG experience that brings the genre into a modern military setting for the first time. In the wake of a devastating pandemic that sweeps through New York City, basic services fail one by one, and without access to food or water, the city quickly descends into chaos. As an agent of The Division, you&#39;ll specialize, modify, and level up your gear, weapons, and skills to take back New York on your own terms.','e4a02a70-fc60-11e5-b8d9-a088697ea576.jpg',36);
INSERT INTO item(item_id,store_id,item_name,price,description,photo,remain) VALUES ('i57','s1','Forza Horizon 2 (Xbox One) - Walmart.com',45.10,'Race through a wide-open world featuring dramatic weather and day to night cycles. Instantly connect with friends in the ultimate celebration of speed, style, and actionpackeddriving. Explore beautiful and exotic locations in more than 200 of the world&#39;s greatest cars, all created with precise detail in 1080p.','e540b030-fc60-11e5-b6db-a088697ea576.jpg',38);
